<h2> Definition </h2>

@KJ{{five}}@KJ{{grade}} verbs form the volitional by changing the final kana to the @HI{{o}}-row
and adding the suffix @HI{{u}}.
<p></p>

@KJ{{ichi}}@KJ{{grade}} verbs form the volitional by dropping the final @HI{{ru}}
and adding the suffix @HI{{you}}.
<p></p>

The two irregular verbs conjugate as shown above.
<p></p>

